        ### [\$partnerTwoPreferredName\$]{.shiny-magenta}

        **If you get close, you can call her / him / them:** [\$partnerTwoNameForClosedCircle\$]{.shiny}

        **You know that one morning he/she/they:** [\$partnerTwoMorning\$]{.shiny}

        **Your partner needs you, she/he/they would like to:** [\$partnerTwoWhatDoYouWantFromPartner\$]{.shiny}

