        Remember, your partners need you as much as you need them

        ## Intimate infrastructure of your communication

        The beginning for your communication will be telegrams. ere are the contacts of your water partners:

        **[\$partnerOnePreferredName\$]{.shiny-magenta}** [\$partnerOneTelegram\$]{.shiny}

        **[\$partnerTwoPreferredName\$]{.shiny-magenta}** [\$partnerTwoTelegram\$]{.shiny}

        Your connection with each partner is unique and individual. Do not mix these connections, let them develop separately from each other, since everyone needs different communication, attention & lines of thought and each of your partners needs a personal approach.

        You can contact them individually on **WEDNESDAY June 24**. As soon as you contact, the game will begin

        Then you can decide how to continue your communication, in a telegram or somewhere else, exchange messages, video calls, [you-and-me]{.shiny} [voice channel in Discord](https://discord.com/invite/n5JBf8x){.shiny} (for that you might need [Instruction how to use it](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1mY2nBkpYQM9JLpISi-L6JJW02TYJaexmDyBCxR21w7U/edit?usp=sharing)). Maybe you want to go through one of the [instructions](http://workhardplay.pw/en/2020/instructions.html) together, watch [a video work](http://workhardplay.pw/en/2020/screenings.html) synchronously, or for you it will become a friendly conversation where you can discuss anything and share your secrets.

        You can also use the option to send a gift to your partner by mail:

        **[\$partnerOnePreferredName\$]{.shiny-magenta}** [\$partnerOneAddress\$]{.shiny}

        **[\$partnerTwoPreferredName\$]{.shiny-magenta}** [\$partnerTwoAddress\$]{.shiny}

